<template>
  <v-dialog v-model="dialog" persistent max-width="290" >
    <v-card>
      <v-card-title class="text-h5 primary">
        Warning
      </v-card-title>

      <v-card-text>
        憑證金額不夠，請申請憑證
      </v-card-text>

      <v-divider></v-divider>

      <v-card-actions>
        <v-spacer></v-spacer>
        <v-btn color="primary" text @click.native="close"> 知道了 </v-btn>
      </v-card-actions>
    </v-card>
  </v-dialog>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    data () {
      return {
        dialog: true,
      }
    },
    methods: {
        close() {
        this.$emit('update:dialog', false)
      }
    }
  };
</script>

<style>
</style>
